reviewText: This is my favorite Chick Fight DVD. Having Lacey, Rain, Ms. Chif, Mercedes Martinez & Cheerleader Melissa all part of the show makes it more than worth the cost. However, the highlight of this DVD is a three way matchup later on between, Ms. Chif, Melissa & Mercedes. It was a wild melee going on all over Kezar Pavilion.  I thoroughly enjoyed it.
